{"parents": [{"link": "../../../", "title": "Finance"}, {"link": "../../", "title": "Guides"}], "prev": {"link": "../add_a_check_request/", "title": "Adding a Check Request"}, "next": {"link": "../add_an_expense/", "title": "Adding an Expense"}, "title": "Adding a Reimbursement", "meta": {}, "body": "<div class=\"section\" id=\"adding-a-reimbursement\">\n<h1>Adding a Reimbursement<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#adding-a-reimbursement\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h1>\n<div class=\"admonition note\">\n<p class=\"admonition-title\">Note</p>\n<p>When you make a purchase with your own money for work-related expenses that should be reimbursed, you should record this by adding a new reimbursement.</p>\n</div>\n<ol class=\"arabic simple\">\n<li><p>Click the &lt;i class=\u201dfa fa-bars\u201d&gt;&lt;/i&gt; <strong>menu icon</strong> in the ribbon</p></li>\n<li><p>Click <strong>Finance</strong></p></li>\n<li><p>Click <strong>Expenses</strong></p></li>\n<li><p>Click <strong>Items</strong></p></li>\n<li><p>Click the &lt;i class=\u201dfa fa-plus\u201d&gt;&lt;/i&gt; <strong>plus icon</strong> in the upper right hand corner</p></li>\n<li><p>Click <strong>Reimbursement</strong></p></li>\n<li><p>Select date of purchase</p></li>\n<li><p>Choose a vendor</p></li>\n<li><p><a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/general/guides/how_to_upload_a_file.html\">Upload</a> a receipt</p></li>\n<li><p>Enter total</p></li>\n<li><p>Click <strong>Save</strong></p></li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n", "metatags": "", "rellinks": [["genindex", "General Index", "I", "index"], ["users/finance/guides/items/add_an_expense", "Adding an Expense", "N", "next"], ["users/finance/guides/items/add_a_check_request", "Adding a Check Request", "P", "previous"]], "sourcename": "users/finance/guides/items/add_a_reimbursement.rst.txt", "toc": "<ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#\">Adding a Reimbursement</a></li>\n</ul>\n", "display_toc": false, "page_source_suffix": ".rst", "current_page_n